'''斯特凡·桑德林'''（{{lang-de|Stefan Sanderling}}，{{bd|1964年|8月2日}}）<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.sptimes.com/2003/09/21/Floridian/Tearing_down_the_walls.shtml | title=Tearing down the walls | work=St. Petersburg Times | author=John Fleming | date=2003-09-21 | accessdate=2007-01-11 | archive-date=2005-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051201165446/http://www.sptimes.com/2003/09/21/Floridian/Tearing_down_the_walls.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>，德国[[指挥家|指挥家]]。生于[[东德|东德]][[东柏林|东柏林]]，是指挥家[[库尔特·桑德林|库尔特·桑德林]]和[[低音提琴|低音提琴]]演奏家芭芭拉·桑德林的儿子。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.sptimes.com/2005/03/04/Artsandentertainment/Sanderling_to_conduct.shtml | title=Sanderling to conduct his family | work=St. Petersburg Times | author=John Fleming | date=2005-03-04 | accessdate=2007-01-11 | archive-date=2005-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051029221550/http://www.sptimes.com/2005/03/04/Artsandentertainment/Sanderling_to_conduct.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>他同父异母的哥哥是指挥家[[托马斯·桑德林|托马斯·桑德林]]。他的弟弟[[米夏埃尔·桑德林|米夏埃尔·桑德林]]是一名[[大提琴|大提琴]]家和指挥家。

== 生平 ==
桑德林年轻时曾演奏过[[钢琴|钢琴]]和[[单簧管|单簧管]]。他早期的大学经历是在德国的[[萨勒河畔哈雷|哈雷]]。在{{tsl|en|Los Angeles Philharmonic Institute|洛杉矶爱乐学院}}，桑德林师从指挥家{{tsl|en|Leonard Slatkin|伦纳德·斯拉特金}}、[[尤里·哈图耶维奇·捷米尔卡诺夫|尤里·特米尔卡诺夫]]、[[艾度·迪華特|艾度·迪華特]]和{{tsl|en|John Nelson (conductor)|约翰·纳尔逊}}。后来，他进入[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]{{tsl|en|USC Thornton School of Music|南加州大学桑顿音乐学院|桑顿音乐学院}}，师从{{tsl|en|Daniel Lewis (conductor)|丹尼尔·刘易斯 (指挥)|丹尼尔·刘易斯}}。他还曾在[[莱比锡|莱比锡]]音乐学院跟随[[库尔特·马苏尔|库尔特·马苏尔]]学习。

桑德林的第一个职业岗位是在[[德国|德国]][[波茨坦|波茨坦]]。此外，他还担任过{{tsl|en|Staatstheater Mainz|美因茨国立剧院}}和{{tsl|en|Philharmonisches Staatsorchester Mainz|美因茨爱乐乐团}}的音乐总监。1996年，他成为[[布列塔尼大區|布列塔尼]]管弦乐团的首席指挥，并担任这一职务直至2003-2004乐季结束。

在美国，桑德林于2002年5月被任命为{{tsl|en|Florida Orchestra|佛罗里达管弦乐团}}的音乐总监，<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.stpetersburgtimes.com/2002/07/19/TampaBay/Seeking_a_home_in_key.shtml | title=Seeking a home in key of charm | work=St. Petersburg Times | author=John Fleming | date=2002-07-19 | access-date=2007-01-11  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060828200930/http://www.stpetersburgtimes.com/2002/07/19/TampaBay/Seeking_a_home_in_key.shtml | archive-date=2006-08-28 | df= }}</ref>并在2003-2004乐季正式担任这一职务。2006年6月，桑德林与佛罗里达乐团续约至2010-2011乐季。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/4713.html | title=Stefan Sanderling Extends Contract with Florida Orchestra | work=Playbill Arts | author=Vivien Schweitzer | date=2006-06-08 | accessdate=2007-01-11 | archive-date=2006-12-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061211144045/http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/4713.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>他的合同进一步延长至2013-2014乐季，此时他计划结束其佛罗里达乐团的任期。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/stefan-sanderling-wont-be-renewing-his-contract-with-the-florida-orchestra/1171996 | title=Stefan Sanderling won't be renewing his contract with the Florida Orchestra | work=Tampa Bay Times | author=John Fleming | date=2011-05-27 | access-date=2012-07-08  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924133626/http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/stefan-sanderling-wont-be-renewing-his-contract-with-the-florida-orchestra/1171996 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | df= }}</ref>有报道称，桑德林与乐团管理层之间在财务和节目方面的冲突是导致他离职的原因。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/article1199547.ece | title=A farewell tour | work=Tampa Bay Times | author=John Fleming | date=2011-11-06 | accessdate=2012-07-08 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20130204072509/http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/article1199547.ece | archive-date=2013-02-04 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tampabay.com/things-to-do/music/stefan-sanderling-talks-exit-return-future/2108227 | title=Stefan Sanderling talks exit, return, future | work=Tampa Bay Times | author=John Fleming | date=2013-03-11 | accessdate=2017-05-29 | archive-date=2019-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415075745/http://www.tampabay.com/things-to-do/music/stefan-sanderling-talks-exit-return-future/2108227 | dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，2012年6月，乐团宣布桑德林在2011-2012乐季结束后提前结束佛罗里达乐团的任期。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/florida-orchestras-stefan-sanderling-stepping-down-early-as-music-director/1237915 | title=Florida Orchestra's Stefan Sanderling stepping down early as music director | work=Tampa Bay Times | author=John Fleming | date=2012-07-02 | accessdate=2012-07-08 | archive-date=2012-07-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120708084753/http://www.tampabay.com/features/performingarts/florida-orchestras-stefan-sanderling-stepping-down-early-as-music-director/1237915 | dead-url=no }}</ref>他和乐团的最后一次亮相是在2014年5月。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.tampabay.com/things-to-do/music/stefan-sanderling-talks-music-art-and-italy-before-final-florida-orchestra/2170815 | title=Stefan Sanderling talks music, art and Italy before final Florida Orchestra performance | work=Tampa Bay Times | author=Stephanie Hayes | date=2014-03-18 | accessdate=2017-05-29 | archive-date=2019-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415075745/http://www.tampabay.com/things-to-do/music/stefan-sanderling-talks-music-art-and-italy-before-final-florida-orchestra/2170815 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在美国，桑德林于2002年成为{{tsl|en|Toledo Symphony Orchestra|托莱多交响乐团}}的首席客座指挥，最初的合同为期两年。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.toledoblade.com/Music-Theater-Dance/2002/07/11/Stefan-Sanderling-signs-a-two-year-pact-with-Toledo-orchestra.html | title=Stefan Sanderling signs a two-year pact with Toledo orchestra | work=Toledo Blade | author=Steven Cornelius | date=2002-07-11 | accessdate=2017-06-12 | archive-date=2017-10-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030221547/http://www.toledoblade.com/Music-Theater-Dance/2002/07/11/Stefan-Sanderling-signs-a-two-year-pact-with-Toledo-orchestra.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>随后，乐团将他的头衔提升为首席指挥，他担任这一职务至2016-2017乐季。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.sent-trib.com/arts_and_entertainment/local_a_e/b-sanderling-ends--year-tenure-as-toledo-symphony-s/article_59c56e56-d67c-58c9-ba58-575e30006968.html | title=Sanderling ends 15-year tenure as Toledo Symphony's principal conductor | work=Sentinel-Tribune | author= | date=2017-04-27 | accessdate=2017-05-29 | archive-date=2017-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427101301/http://www.sent-trib.com/arts_and_entertainment/local_a_e/b-sanderling-ends--year-tenure-as-toledo-symphony-s/article_59c56e56-d67c-58c9-ba58-575e30006968.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年5月，作为“音乐之春”音乐节的一部分，桑德林指挥托莱多交响乐团进行了乐团在卡内基音乐厅的首演。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/09/arts/music/orpheus-and-toledo-symphony-at-carnegie-hall-review.html | title=Something Borrowed and Something New | work=New York Times | author=James R Oestreich | date=2011-05-08 | accessdate=2017-05-29 | archive-date=2018-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519120937/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/09/arts/music/orpheus-and-toledo-symphony-at-carnegie-hall-review.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>桑德林在2008年夏季演出季开始时成为了{{tsl|en|Chautauqua Symphony Orchestra|肖托夸交响乐团}}的音乐总监，担任这个职位一直到2011年。

2015年9月，桑德林被任命为[[列支敦士登|列支敦士登]]交响乐团下一任首席指挥，从2016-2017乐季开始生效。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lie-zeit.li/2015/09/stefan-sanderling-neuer-sol-chefdirigent/|title=Stefan Sanderling neuer SOL-Chefdirigent|work=Lie Zeit|author=|date=2015-09-15|accessdate=2017-06-12|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825161337/http://www.lie-zeit.li/2015/09/stefan-sanderling-neuer-sol-chefdirigent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
桑德林的妻子是大提琴家伊莎贝尔·贝桑松（{{lang-fr|Isabelle Besançon}}），她曾在他们相识的布列塔尼管弦乐团演奏。他们于2002年11月结婚。2002年12月31日，在[[雷蒙詹姆斯体育场|雷蒙詹姆斯体育场]]发生了一起事件，这对夫妻本应作为客人在一场[[美式足球|美式橄榄球]]比赛中与[[坦帕|坦帕]]商人大卫·哈伯特见面。受到[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]后安全问题加剧的影响，一名保安阻止贝桑松进入体育场，因为她的钱包过大。据报道，事件之所以升级，是因为一名保安表示，他“不能冒险让这对夫妇进去，因为他们是外国人”。此事在坦帕体育局通讯总监芭芭拉·凯茜给桑德林的道歉信中得到解决。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.sptimes.com/2003/01/10/TampaBay/Maestro_s_football_ou.shtml | title=Maestro's football outing hits sour note | work=St. Petersburg Times | author=John Fleming | date=2003-01-01 | accessdate=2007-01-11 | archive-date=2006-03-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060325163515/http://www.sptimes.com/2003/01/10/TampaBay/Maestro_s_football_ou.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

